ğŸ§  Memories Implemented (Langchain_memory.ipynb)

BufferMemory â†’ Full-context customer support chats

BufferWindowMemory â†’ Lightweight FAQ bot (last 3 messages only)

TokenBufferMemory â†’ Summarization bot without hitting token/context limits

SummaryMemory â†’ Assistant that turns long conversations into recap notes

ğŸ”— Chains Built (L3_chains.ipynb)

